      "code_changes": [
        {
          "content": "{\n  \"files\": [\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/webidl/Request.webidl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/fetch/Request.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/fetch/Request.cpp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/webidl/Response.webidl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/fetch/Response.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/fetch/Response.cpp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/webidl/Headers.webidl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/fetch/Headers.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/fetch/Headers.cpp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/webidl/FetchEvent.webidl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerEvents.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"mozilla-firefox/firefox\",\n      \"path\": \"dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerEvents.cpp\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"text\": \"Found all Fetch API WebIDL interface definitions and their corresponding C++ binding implementations:\\n\\n**Request Interface:**\\n- WebIDL: dom/webidl/Request.webidl defines the Request interface per the WHATWG Fetch specification\\n- C++ Header: dom/fetch/Request.h contains the class Request final which implements the WebIDL Request interface\\n- C++ Implementation: dom/fetch/Request.cpp contains the implementation of Request methods\\n\\n**Response Interface:**\\n- WebIDL: dom/webidl/Response.webidl defines the Response interface per the WHATWG Fetch specification\\n- C++ Header: dom/fetch/Response.h contains the class Response final which implements the WebIDL Response interface\\n- C++ Implementation: dom/fetch/Response.cpp contains the implementation of Response methods\\n\\n**Headers Interface:**\\n- WebIDL: dom/webidl/Headers.webidl defines the Headers interface per the WHATWG Fetch specification\\n- C++ Header: dom/fetch/Headers.h contains the class Headers final which implements the WebIDL Headers interface\\n- C++ Implementation: dom/fetch/Headers.cpp contains the implementation of Headers methods\\n\\n**FetchEvent Interface:**\\n- WebIDL: dom/webidl/FetchEvent.webidl defines the FetchEvent interface as part of the Service Worker specification, extending ExtendableEvent\\n- C++ Header: dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerEvents.h contains the class FetchEvent final which implements the WebIDL FetchEvent interface\\n- C++ Implementation: dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerEvents.cpp contains the implementation of FetchEvent methods\\n\\nThe mapping shows that Request, Response, and Headers implementations are co-located in dom/fetch/ while FetchEvent implementation is in dom/serviceworkers/ since FetchEvent is specific to Service Worker functionality.\"\n}\n",
